      "title": "Thousands in line for Gas as shortage worsens",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Laugfs and Litro gas still have NOT been able to meet the market demand.",
        "However, Litro Gas said that two vessels carrying 7,000 MT of gas will reach the country between the 5th and 12th of July 2022.",
        "Long queues were be seen in many areas in the country for laugfs gas across the country.",
        "Several tense situations had taken place in several areas due to the lack of gas.",
        "Committee probing recent riots obtains statement from fmr Army Commander"
